        <abstract> 
<p>Criticises the Duke of Argyll’s book [<hi rend="italic">Reign of law</hi> (1867)], particularly on sexual selection.</p> 
            <p>But CD overlooks God’s intention to instruct man by nature’s beauty.</p> 
<p>Criticism of anonymous article in <hi rend="italic">North British Review</hi> [by Fleeming Jenkin, 46 (1867): 277–318].</p> 
            <p>CK supports large sports in response to large environmental changes.</p>
        </abstract>
